'''Bithuband''' was a musician's guild and booking agency. Shortly before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] they were based in [[CoCo Town/Legends|CoCo Town]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], and specialized in [[Bith/Legends|Bith]] musicians. The Bithuband displayed an advertisement on the [[HoloNet News/Legends|HoloNet News]] in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]].

